# Bitcoin Stamps Indexer Code Style Guidelines

This document details code style and quality guidelines for the Bitcoin Stamps Indexer project.

## Formatting

- Use Black with a maximum line length of 127 characters.
- Sort imports using isort.

## Linting

- Run flake8, ignoring the following codes:
  - E203
  - W503
  - E402
  - E501

## Type Checking

- Use Mypy to enforce type hints across the codebase.

## Pre-commit Hooks

A `.pre-commit-config.yaml` at the repository root is configured to run:
- black  
- isort  
- flake8  
- mypy  
- pytest (basic smoke tests)
